description:
**Goal:** Define core mount data types

**Files:** src/app_state.rs

**Steps:**
1. Define DriveId (UUID wrapper or newtype)
2. Define DriveConfig { id, label, server_hostname, server_ethernet_ip, share_name, username, mount_point, enabled }
3. Define DriveStatus enum { Disconnected, Mounting, Connected { via, ip }, Reconnecting { from, to }, Error(String) }
4. Define AdhocMount { host, share, mount_point, via }

**Done when:** Types compile and are used in AppState
